---
description: Backend, database, and API rules
globs:
  - src/api/**/*
  - src/lib/**/*
alwaysApply: false
---

- RLS required on every Supabase table — never skip or bypass
- Always use Supabase Auth — no custom JWT implementation
- Default to SQL for deterministic queries — no LLM for structured data
- LLM calls only for approved features listed in project.mdc
- All API responses must match contracts in tech-spec.md
